about.description: Collection of algorithms and functions for ultrafast electron diffraction.
about.summary: Collection of algorithms and functions for ultrafast electron diffraction

name: scikit-ued
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.0.1" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash_value = "3f559389ba61aaa8098bf346dd3dc4bb79ad0e74d208b3957d794a46d492b705" %}

package:
  name: 'scikit-ued'
  version: '{{ version }}'

source:
  fn: 'scikit-ued-{{ version }}.tar.gz'
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/s/scikit-ued/scikit-ued-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  '{{ hash_type }}': '{{ hash_value }}'

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - numpy >=1.13, <2
    - scipy >=1.0.0, <2
    - scikit-image >=0.15, <1
    - tifffile >=0.13, <1
    - pywavelets >=1.0.0, <2
    - crystals >=0.6.5, <1
    - npstreams >=1.6, <2
    - pyyaml >=3.1, <4

test:
  imports:
    - skued

about:
  home: https://github.com/LaurentRDC/scikit-ued
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: 'LICENSE.txt'
  summary: Collection of algorithms and functions for ultrafast electron diffraction
  description: Collection of algorithms and functions for ultrafast electron diffraction.
  doc_url: https://scikit-ued.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: 'https://github.com/LaurentRDC/scikit-ued'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers: 
    - LaurentRDC
